-- Dotnetcore runtime installation steps in linux (ubuntu) --

Install prerequisites from dotnetcore runtime 
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/core/linux-prerequisites.

Download install scripts 
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/core/tools/dotnet-install-script

Run below cmd to install runtime
sudo ./dotnet-install.sh --install-dir /usr/bin/dotnet --shared-runtime --version 1.1.2

Add global environment PATH variable to access dotnet system wide
Append /usr/bin/dotnet this path in /etc/environment file

Reboot the system

To Check :- hit dotnet it will show dotnet installed details.
